OL,6,FRachel Bullock went to meet a family
OL,7,Fwho have shared their story of loss
OL,8,Ffor a stop-smoking TV campaign
OL,10,FA family from Hartlepool are fronting
OL,11,Fa 'quit smoking' campaign after
OL,12,Fexperiencing their own loss as a
OL,13,Fresult of the habit.
OL,15,FThe North East once had the highest
OL,16,Fnumber of smokers in the country, and
OL,17,Fwhile hard campaigning has reduced the
OL,18,Fscale of it, two out of three smokers
OL,19,Fwill die as a result of smoking.
