OL,6,FDenham Thomas was one of those people.
OL,7,FHe had his first cigarette aged 10 and
OL,8,Fhis death was from a disease directly
OL,9,Flinked to tobacco.
OL,11,FHis widow, daughter and granddaughter
OL,12,Fare now featuring in a TV advertising
OL,13,Fcampaign to urge others to quit before
OL,14,Fit is too late.
OL,16,FRecalling some of Denham's final
OL,17,Fmoments, his bereaved wife Debbie told
OL,18,FITV Tyne Tees: "The consultant came
OL,19,Fout and she said she put him on end of
OL,20,Flife and he couldn't believe it he
OL,21,Fsaid 'What at the end of life?'
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
