OL,6,F"He said, 'that's a load of rubbish,
OL,7,Fit can't be the end of life'. He
OL,8,F(later) passed away at home
OL,9,Fpeacefully."
OL,11,FA former fitness instructor, Denham
OL,12,Fwas diagnosed with COPD aged 35 and
OL,13,Fspent the next 20 years hooked up to
OL,14,Foxygen and in a wheelchair.
OL,16,FHis daughter Sadie, who was a champion
OL,17,Fboxer in her teenage years, said she
OL,18,Fdid not remember her dad ever being
OL,19,Fwell, while Debbie became his carer.
