OL,6,FHoping their awful loss at the very
OL,7,Fleast leads others to quit, Debbie and
OL,8,FSadie decided to take part in a new TV
OL,9,Fadvert, which includes the footage of
OL,10,FDenham.
OL,12,FThe message? "Stop smoking now."
OL,14,FSpeaking about her involvement, Sadie
OL,15,Fsaid: "I'm absolutely over the moon
OL,16,Fand I think he would be thrilled that
OL,17,Fwe've been a part of something that he
OL,18,Freally believed in.
OL,20,F"And even if it inspires one person,
OL,21,Fthat's done its job.
