OL,6,F"The less people are affected by
OL,7,Fsmoking, the better, really, and the
OL,8,Fless families that are affected in the
OL,9,Fin the long run."
OL,11,FThe North East once had the highest
OL,12,Fnumber of smokers in the country,
OL,13,Fprompting the creation of specialist
OL,14,Fcharity - Fresh.
OL,16,FThese adverts are part of their
OL,17,Fcampaign.
OL,19,FThe charity's found that here, 13.1
OL,20,Fper cent of people still smoke, that
OL,21,Faround 270,000 of us.
