OL,6,FAnd almost two out of three long term
OL,7,Fsmokers will die from a smoking
OL,8,Frelated condition.
OL,10,FAilsa Rutter, from Fresh Smoking
OL,11,FCessation Service, said: "These
OL,12,Fcampaigns are really important, but on
OL,13,Ftheir own they're not a magic solution.
OL,15,F"That's why we must have lots of other
OL,16,Fthings happening - the really
OL,17,Fimportant role of our Stop Smoking
OL,18,FServices. This is still our biggest
OL,19,Fcause of health inequalities."
