OL,6,FThis tv campaign is focussing on more
OL,7,Fthan just the smoking fatality rate.
OL,9,F"It is about that terrible impact it
OL,10,Fhas," added Ailsa, "and for their
OL,11,Floved ones as well. You feel so
OL,12,Fhelpless."
